# Customer API Test Requests

### List all customers
GET http://localhost:3000/api/customers HTTP/1.1

### Get a single customer by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/customers/1 HTTP/1.1

### Create a new customer
POST http://localhost:3000/api/customers HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "phone": "555-9999"
}

### Update an existing customer
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/customers/1 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alice Johnson Updated",
  "email": "alice.new@example.com"
}

### Delete a customer
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/customers/5 HTTP/1.1
